td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation, on the one hand, of Clause 4 of the framework agreement on part-time work, concluded on 6 June 1997 (‘the Framework Agreement’), which is set out in the Annex to Council Directive 97/81/EC of 15 December 1997 concerning the Framework Agreement on part-time work concluded by UNICE, CEEP and the ETUC (
OJ 1998 L 14, p. 9
) and, on the other hand, of Article 4 of Council Directive 79/7/EEC of 19 December 1978 on the progressive implementation of the principle of equal treatment for men and women in matters of social security (
OJ 1979 L 6, p. 24
).
